snippet.title: [PS1] Milano no Arubaito - RPG/mini-games collection from Westone
snippet.description: Milano no Arubaito is a mini-games collection from Westone(the creators of the Wonder Boy series) with light role-playing elements and gorgeous spritework. Earn money by taking on a variety of increasingly difficult jobs and spend it on new furniture, plants and electrical appliances for Milano's house.
